doc.after: From 1842 the boundaries of the city were comprehended by the baronies of Dublin City and the Barony of Dublin In 1930 the boundaries were extended by the Local Government Dublin Act 23 Later in 1953 the boundaries were again extended by the Local Government Provisional Order Confirmation Act 24
